dct_title_s: Land between Mantua Creek and Little Mantua Creek
dct_description_sm: Shows area between Mantua Creek and Little Mantua Creek.
Shows land now or formally under tidewater situate granted and quitclaimed to Shell Oil Company. Shows pierhead and bulkhead lines, New Jersey Route 130, and easements of land.
